<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My Top 10 Favorite Anime</title>

    <style>
        body{
            font-family: Arial;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1{
            color: darkblue;
        }

        .container{
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card{
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid pink;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .card img{
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .card h3{
            color: darkred;
        }

        .card p{
            font-size: 13px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <h1>MY TOP 10 FAVORITE ANIME</h1>

    <div class="container">

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 1</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/60/Naruto_Anime.jpg">
            <p><b>Naruto</b><br>Popular ninja anime full of action and friendship.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 2</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/9a/One_Piece_Logo.png">
            <p><b>One Piece</b><br>An adventure anime about pirates searching for treasure.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 3</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/c/c3/Attack_on_Titan_Season_1.jpg">
            <p><b>Attack on Titan</b><br>Humans fight giant Titans to survive.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 4</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/7/72/Demon_Slayer_Kimetsu_no_Yaiba_logo.svg">
            <p><b>Demon Slayer</b><br>A boy fights demons to save his sister.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 5</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/e1/Jujutsu_kaisen.jpg">
            <p><b>Jujutsu Kaisen</b><br>Students battle powerful curses using magic.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 6</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/0/0b/Death_Note_Vol_1.jpg">
            <p><b>Death Note</b><br>A smart student finds a deadly notebook.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 7</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/46/Dragon_Ball_Super_Key_visual.jpg">
            <p><b>Dragon Ball</b><br>Goku protects Earth with powerful battles.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 8</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/95/My_Hero_Academia_Season_1.jpg">
            <p><b>My Hero Academia</b><br>Young heroes train to save the world.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 9</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/6/6f/Tokyo_Ghoul_volume_1_cover.jpg">
            <p><b>Tokyo Ghoul</b><br>A student becomes half-human and half-ghoul.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Top 10</h3>
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/5/52/Spy_x_Family_volume_1_cover.jpg">
            <p><b>Spy x Family</b><br>A funny family with secret identities.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>

